{"tid":272525,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【無牙老虎】被證監指令停牌 隆成金融今早偷雞交易5秒","createTime":"2017-06-06T01:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T01:56:20.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e87a79fe5f793b765c1a5cc038c3f8f9e774b52f","tid":272525,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170606/large/1496712883_ddfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170606%2Flarge%2F1496712883_ddfe.jpg&h=630e699b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚發公告表示被證監指令停牌的隆成金融（1225），今早無視證監指令，無停牌繼續在股市交易，在開市前已有一宗成交，在開市後五秒內亦有六宗成交，五秒後才正式停牌。即有人疑似無視證監權力，偷步沽貨離場。該股在停牌前停9.28%，報0.127元，成交股數98.8萬股，成交金額12.62萬元。<br />\n<br />\n隆成金融昨晚表示，指接獲證監會函件，被要求今早停牌，原因是證監會指其2015年有關宣佈之公開發售之通函有重大失實、不完整或錯誤引導資料，停牌符合投資大眾或公眾之利益。<br />\n<br />\n上月中，被稱為「股壇長毛」的資深投資者David Webb在其網站發表「迷之網絡：50只不能買的港股」（The Enigma Network: 50 stocks not to own），文章附圖列出50只港股，指部份股份是泡沫，已被證監警告股權過度集中；另外部份股份則是公司管理層為自身利益，刻意持有這些泡沫股。亦有部份股份上榜原因是公司有大量投資，但投資權益披露不足，其中一隻就是隆成金融。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56789289&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56789289%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170606&d=hfn5yKhbSVEtCsImkGIkGDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=949548e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56789289%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170606&h=8f952f18\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56789289&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170606</a>"},{"pid":"ad5af8082b4d5c526636bd04d08bab9902360e4e","tid":272525,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T01:56:20.000Z","msg":"SFC唔係有權要求還原交易咩?"}]}